Description
-----------

This package contains implementation of external memory algorithm
computing the LZ77 factorization called EM-LZscan from the paper

  Juha Karkkainen, Dominik Kempa and Simon J. Puglisi,
  Lempel-Ziv Parsing in External Memory.
  In Proc. DCC 2014.


Compilation and usage
---------------------

Compilation is done with the Makefile provided in the src/ directory.

$ cd src
$ make

The encode_lz77 program encodes the given file using LZ77 method,
decode_lz77 decodes the file back to original. Run program without
parameter for exact syntax.


Terms of use
------------

If you use this code, please cite the paper mentioned above and publish
the URL from which you downloaded the code.



Helsinki, Feb 2016.
